Package com.tangosol.util.comparator

Class ExtractorComparator<T>

java.lang.Object
com.tangosol.util.comparator.ExtractorComparator<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
ExternalizableLite, PortableObject, Serializable, Comparator<T>
public class ExtractorComparator<T> extends Object implements Comparator<T>, ExternalizableLite, PortableObject
Comparator implementation that uses specified ValueExtractor to extract value(s) to be used for comparison.

as 2010.09.09
